getSpawnPosition

public static com.sun.darkstar.example.snowman.common.util.Coordinate getSpawnPosition(String map,
                                                                                       com.sun.darkstar.example.snowman.common.protocol.enumn.ETeamColor team,
                                                                                       int player,
                                                                                       int teamPlayers)
Return the player'th spawn position for the given team on the given map assuming there are totalPlayers per team. This method will return positions equidistant from eachother along the X axis and at a fixed Y coordinate.

Parameters:
map - name of the map
team - team to retrieve a spawn point for
player - player'th player on the team (starting with 1)
teamPlayers - number of players on the team
Returns:
a spawn position for the player
